Namtatay Sa Ingay - Namtatay Sa Ingay demo
Namtatay Sa Ingay - Namtatay Sa Ingay demo

Originally ripped by Terminal Escape, posted on June 23, 2015 Description from Terminal Escape:
Fierce hardcore - more than the simple sum of parts and certainly more power than any description from me could indicate, New York's NAMATAY SA INGAY ride a sharp blade for the entire ten minutes of their first demo. I hope to see them when they pay SF a visit next month, I can only imagine that they are every bit as intense live.... NAMATAY SA INGAY Released by the Bay Area's Aklasan Records, an excellent source for info on the growing Filipino American hardcore/punk scene, and the fest coming up next month...
